    <intervention_name>Intra-articular Ropivacaine injection</intervention_name>
    <description>The procedure will be done by the surgeon at the end of the operation, with an intra-articular injection of 20 ml 0.75% Ropivacaine through the arthroscopic cannula after closure of the anterior wound</description>
